==Trivia==
* It is still possible to skip Vet'ion's second phase as of 6 Jan 2026.
* Vet'ion's 2014 model was an enlarged, re-coloured version of [[Ranalph Devere]] from the [[Legends' Quest]].
* Vet'ion's examine is a reference to Tolkien's ''{{WP|The Return of the King}}''.
* Vet'ion's name is an anagram of {{RSL|Novite equipment|Novite}} from ''RuneScape 3''.
** Vet'ion's armour in his normal form matches the colour of Novite armour (tier 1) and the recolour in his enraged form matches {{RSL|Primal equipment|Primal armour}} (tier 99), both found within {{RSL|Daemonheim}} (located in the Wilderness).

